This template should be placed at the top of an section, linking the reader to articles that contain details of a topic, which is summarized in the section only (related content).

==Usage==

 <nowiki>{{EntirePage|otherpage}}</nowiki>

* '''otherpage''': Name of the page, which was summarized by the section (appears as link then).

==Example==

 <nowiki>{{EntirePage|:Category:Templates}}</nowiki>
turns into
<blockquote>''For the entire article, see [[:Category:Templates]].''</blockquote>

[[Category:Templates]]
